Luckily the serum works for any skin type! You can find the Brightening Saffron Serum at your local Sephora, your skin will thank you!

Building a life I’ll look back and be proud of.

Being intentional with where//who I pour my time and energy into has been a huge priority heading into the end of the year. This for me has looked like making more of a conscious effort to take consistent action day by day towards my goals and pouring more back into the people I love (some days are better than others, learning to give myself grace). 2024 and beyond will be the year I balance my time to nourish every area of my life, whether it be my mental & physical health, my relationships, or my personal goals — I’m heading into the New Year with a new found purpose. 🧡

What’re somethings you plan on doing heading into the New Year? LMK! 

#lifestyle #fashion #vlogger #minivlog #selfcare #motivation #mensfashion #ootd #skincare #menshealth #healthyhabits #fitness #dayinthelife

The year of no fear 🧧

This time, last year, marks the first anniversary of taking digital media seriously and if you’ve been following me since, you know I’ve been hustling from 0-100. 2023 was an extraordinary year in all aspects, the lows and the highs have brought me so much growth, peace, and clarity. I placed the biggest bet on myself, made content creation a full time gig, took on entrepreneurship, and never looked back. This chapter of my life has showed me anything is possible AND attainable if you work smart and stay consistent with your efforts. I’m not sure where the next year+ will take me and I’m quite frightened if we’re being frank, but I’m also very excited to experience it all and do it on my own terms. I hope my journey has helped or served to inspire anyone that’s been tuning in, to put in the time and effort to pursue whatever side hustle you’re passionate about because that’s who I’m doing this for. Put 100% focus and double down for an entire year+ cause you never know where it might take you or the doors it may open. Words can’t describe how immensely grateful I am for the love you’ve shown, it NEVER goes unnoticed. Thank you for changing my life for the better and cheers to more prosperity, good health, and your continuous support. 🫂
